{"tid":1035393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"EVA初號機Metal Build 模型日本開售　疑似中國排隊黨打尖搶籌","createTime":"2019-02-24T14:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T01:52:00.000Z","uid":48083,"like":35,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"af6e6e689a6fce200da9016f9c10df1bc3f35043","tid":1035393,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T14:56:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EaRvZer.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEaRvZer.png&h=ae3c3e25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n崔德興2019-02-24 14<br />\n日本人氣經典動漫《新世紀福音戰士》模型Metal Build EVA 初號機昨日（23日）在日本、香港等地發售，引起Fans瘋狂搶購。然而，網絡流傳有疑似中國「排隊黨」出現在日本的搶購人龍中，而且打尖情況嚴重，有人因為拿不到籌，甚至出手從店員手中搶奪。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bzdm5Uz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBzdm5Uz.png&h=33c4d96d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cZZYoGf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcZZYoGf.png&h=b26e8ea0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rOi2Qmg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrOi2Qmg.png&h=5df609d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本網民控訴疑似中國排隊黨惡行。（Twitter）<br />\n<br />\nMetal Build EVA 初號機日本定價約為2.3萬日元（約1650港元），但市場反應熱烈，一出便激起炒風，網上「炒價」更達逾2500港元。暴利之下，日本東京、大阪亦出現不少「排隊黨」輪候搶購，不少日本網民在Twitter等留言發表不滿，並上傳模型店被疑似中國排隊黨「佔據」的照片。<br />\n<br />\n有日本Twiiter 網民表示，東京秋葉原售賣情況極為混亂，人龍前面部份被疑似中國排隊黨佔領，周圍都聽到「中國語」。也有網民指出，不少疑似中國人插隊，警衛人員勸喻不要插隊時卻反被罵，雙方繼而展開罵戰。<br />\n<br />\n店員派籌的時候變得更加混亂。有網民指出，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有店員要求排隊人士講出商品名稱，才能分發籌券。但部份講不出商品名稱的疑似中國人不明白為何不被發籌，有人圍繞店員大聲恐嚇，甚至出手搶去店員手上的籌。</span></span>而日本網民上傳的照片亦顯示，疑似中國排隊黨成功購入大量貨品，甚至裝滿一架小型貨車。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cOOFB1o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcOOFB1o.png&h=94a6189c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/24/225521_9ce9778a54389393782a81570e642b53.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F24%2F225521_9ce9778a54389393782a81570e642b53.png&h=1eca99d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/24/225523_03a4bf491f51f2e2bf254feed2de367b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F24%2F225523_03a4bf491f51f2e2bf254feed2de367b.png&h=c206abab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/24/225526_81fbfd4367d8cae4b6f6411e91897e65.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F24%2F225526_81fbfd4367d8cae4b6f6411e91897e65.png&h=339a5987&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/24/225530_260a6678983128dcae85f88d524c3929.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F24%2F225530_260a6678983128dcae85f88d524c3929.png&h=1df484e8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/24/225532_42c9ade7599b35361f08e804edfccd43.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F24%2F225532_42c9ade7599b35361f08e804edfccd43.png&h=5fed7215&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/24/225534_81d0889621765f43764634880b37a55f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F24%2F225534_81d0889621765f43764634880b37a55f.png&h=3094a38f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/24/225536_eefddbb873051df1e3b3ec4224cc1100.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F24%2F225536_eefddbb873051df1e3b3ec4224cc1100.png&h=f1f215a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時中國/298835/eva初號機metal-build-模型日本開售-疑似中國排隊黨打尖搶籌?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_li